OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FA man accused of a brutal rape made
OL,7,Fnumerous internet searches including
OL,8,F"why am I sweating" and "how long is
OL,9,FDNA kept in the database" after the
OL,10,Finvestigation was reopened, a court
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FPaul Quinn, 51, is alleged to have
OL,14,Fattacked and raped a woman in her 30s
OL,15,Fwho was beaten and strangled on 19
OL,16,FJuly 2003 in Little Hulton, Salford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
