FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FA year after the attack, another man -
OL,7,F60-year-old Andrew Malkinson - was
OL,8,Fjailed for the alleged crimes,
OL,9,Fbecoming the victim of a "most
OL,10,Fterrible miscarriage of justice",
OL,11,FManchester Crown Court heard.
OL,13,FMr Malkinson spent 17 years behind
OL,14,Fbars, but always denied the charges
OL,15,Fand in 2021 he was finally released.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
