OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FAs Mr Malkinson's long campaign to
OL,7,Fclear his name gathered more
OL,8,Fpublicity, Quinn made multiple
OL,9,Finternet searches about the case,
OL,10,Fprosecutor John Price KC told jurors
OL,11,Fon the second day of the trial.
OL,13,FJurors were told Quinn's internet
OL,14,Fusage showed he had little interest in
OL,15,Ffollowing the news, but showed a great
OL,16,Finterest in Andrew Malkinson's case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FIn July 2022 news broke that police
OL,7,Fhad linked an unknown suspect through
OL,8,FDNA, which had a "profound" effect on
OL,9,FQuinn's internet browsing, the
OL,10,Fprosecutor said.
OL,12,FAnalysis showed Quinn made 89 news
OL,13,Foutlet searches in September 2022, 69
OL,14,Fin October 2022, and 49 in November
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FThe defendant, who was now living in
OL,18,FDevon, visited the Manchester Evening
OL,19,FNews website 249 times between August
OL,20,Fand December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FMr Price told jurors that around the
OL,7,Fsame time Quinn Googled "how long is
OL,8,Fdna kept in database", and "why do i
OL,9,Fkeep sweating all the time..."
OL,11,FOther searches included "Can you
OL,12,Frefuse to give a DNA sample to the
OL,13,Fpolice UK...... Is my DNA in a
OL,14,Fdatabase UK".
OL,16,FMr Price continued: "Why? Why do you
OL,17,Fsee this defendant researching that
OL,18,Fand asking questions, 'How long DNA
OL,19,Fcan be kept by the authorities?'"
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@UO]pD@\OUqD@^O]sD@YOUvD@LO]xD@
