PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FThe defendant, who lived locally to
OL,7,Fthe attack at the time before moving
OL,8,Fsouth, was only linked to the crime
OL,9,Fyears later after scientific advances
OL,10,Fmatched his DNA profile from samples
OL,11,Fleft on the victim.
OL,13,FAfter Quinn was arrested in December
OL,14,F2022, he was asked to explain to
OL,15,Fdetectives how his DNA came to be on
OL,16,Fthe victim and her clothing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
