OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FThe defendant told police at the time
OL,7,Fhis lifestyle, between 1992 and 2010,
OL,8,Fwas to go out partying with friends
OL,9,Fevery weekend, taking drugs and he
OL,10,Fwould be highly promiscuous, having
OL,11,Fsex with two or three women a night,
OL,12,Feach weekend.
OL,14,FIf true, jurors were told, this would
OL,15,Fmean that in those years, he will have
OL,16,Fhad casual sex with about 2,700 local
OL,17,Fwomen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FMr Price said Quinn was trying to
OL,7,Fimply his DNA could be linked to the
OL,8,Frape simply because the victim had
OL,9,Fbeen one of the many women he had sex
OL,10,Fwith.
OL,12,FJurors heard Mr Malkinson first
OL,13,Fappealed against his conviction in
OL,14,F2006, but this was dismissed.
OL,16,FHe then made two more attempts, in
OL,17,F2009 and 2018, to ask the Criminal
OL,18,FCases Review Commission to send his
OL,19,Fcase to the Court of Appeal, but both
OL,20,Ftimes was rejected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
