FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772733968
OL,3,CRape suspect looked up 'miscarriage of
OL,4,Cjustice' after wrong man was jailed
OL,6,FHis final attempt in 2021 led to his
OL,7,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,8,Fallowed by the Court of Appeal.
OL,10,FQuinn has pleaded not guilty to two
OL,11,Fcounts of rape, grievous bodily harm
OL,12,Fand attempting to choke or strangle
OL,13,Fhis victim to render her unconscious
OL,14,Fwhile he carried out the attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
